{
  "script_id": "composite-function",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "一台机器把苹果榨成汁，再来一台机器把汁装进瓶。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "两台机器接力，苹果就一步步变成了瓶装果汁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "函数也能这样接力：一个的输出，正好是另一个的输入。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "这种函数套函数的组合，就叫做复合函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "复合函数记作 f 圈 g，读作 f 复合 g，写成 f(g(x))。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "计算时从里往外：先让内层 g 作用于 x，得到 g(x)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "再把 g(x) 送进外层 f，最终得到 f(g(x))。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "graph",
      "line_id": "gra-1",
      "filename": "graph-gra-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/graph-gra-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "青色是内层 g，橙色是外层 f，粉色才是复合出的新曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "graph",
      "line_id": "gra-2",
      "filename": "graph-gra-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/graph-gra-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "内层先把 x 弯折伸缩，外层再在此基础上二次塑形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "graph",
      "line_id": "gra-3",
      "filename": "graph-gra-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/graph-gra-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "于是粉色曲线的形状，往往和单独任何一条都大不相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "order",
      "line_id": "ord-1",
      "filename": "order-ord-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/order-ord-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "先平方再加一，和先加一再平方，结果并不一样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "order",
      "line_id": "ord-2",
      "filename": "order-ord-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/order-ord-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "一般来说 f 复合 g 不等于 g 复合 f，交换次序会得到不同的函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "选择不同的内层和外层函数，看粉色复合曲线怎样随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.41,
      "size": 38592,
      "text": "点击演示，跟着箭头看某个 x 如何先经 g 再经 f 走完两步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "复合函数把两个函数接力：f(g(x)) 先算内层再算外层。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "次序不可随意交换，f 复合 g 通常不等于 g 复合 f。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "composite-function",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/composite-function/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.55,
      "size": 40752,
      "text": "学会拆解与组合函数，你就掌握了搭建复杂关系的积木，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 37.07,
  "total_size": 592992
}